Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:15.79,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}Chain reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:19.71,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}見つめる Red eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:24.38,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}真理を探していたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:28.72,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}あてもなく彷徨いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:35.31,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1300)\blur3\be3}幾千億の絡み合う Elements
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.35,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}思考の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:40.06,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}揺れている Chaotic town
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.36,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}まるで so Confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.40,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}消えないんだ　Spiritual pain
